'''揭秘计划'''（{{lang-en|The Disclosure Project}}），也译为'''揭秘工程'''，是一个位于[[美国|美国]][[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]的[[非营利组织|非营利组织]]。它是[[外星智慧生命研究中心|外星智慧生命研究中心]]旗下的一个项目，由[[史蒂芬·格里爾|史蒂芬·格里爾]]于1993年发起<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=KUqLKSWPrvQC&pg=PA1 |title=Life With a Cosmos Clearance |first1=Daniel M |last1=Salter |first2=Nancy |last2=Red Star |publisher=Light Technology Publishing |year=2003 |isbn=1891824376 |pages=x–ix, 1–4}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010502193905/http://www.disclosureproject.org/projecthistory.htm| publisher=disclosureproject.org| title=The Disclosure Project - Background|date=2001-04-16}}</ref>，该组织致力于向公众披露[[政府|政府]]对[[UFO|UFO]]、[[外星人|外星人]]、先进[[能源|能源]]与推进系统所了解的真相<ref name="Daily Emerald">{{cite news| title = Alien theorist offers proof of government coverup| last = Schmidt| first = Brad| url = http://dailyemerald.com/2002/04/25/alien-theorist-offers-proof-of-government-coverup/| newspaper = Daily Emerald| date = 25 April 2002| access-date = 2020-07-23| archive-date = 2012-08-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120814040025/http://dailyemerald.com/2002/04/25/alien-theorist-offers-proof-of-government-coverup/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| last = Tudor| first = Silke| title = Alien Culture| newspaper = SF Weekly| date = 26 September 2001| url = http://www.sfweekly.com/2001-09-26/news/alien-culture/| access-date = 2020-07-23| archive-date = 2015-06-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618125730/http://www.sfweekly.com/2001-09-26/news/alien-culture/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。该工程旨在分享与[[不明飞行物|不明飞行物]]有关的内幕消息，[[赦免|赦免]]那些愿意违反安全誓言的政府[[吹哨人|吹哨人]]<ref>{{cite news| title = Admiral: Never looked for UFO data| last = Cox| first = Billy| url = http://www.heraldtribune.com/article/20080806/blog32/525095430| newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune| date = 6 August 2008| access-date = 2020-07-23| archive-date = 2013-09-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130925174053/http://www.heraldtribune.com/article/20080806/blog32/525095430| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

